   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0065"/>Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb467">Seis am Schlern</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb969">Tirol</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0066"/><supplied type="image-description">Schuppen zwischen Bäumen</supplied></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="left"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0065"/><date when="1908-08-09">9. 8. 08</date>.</dateline><salute rend="left">Lieber Freund,</salute></opener><p>Meine <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb17164">Frau</rs> u. ich danken
               Euch herzlich für Eure <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03464-1"/>Glückwün<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03464-1"><ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L03463" subtype="See"/>.
               </note>.</p><p><rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb17164">Wir</rs> rei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en morgen nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb772">Marienbad</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb147567">Haus
                     <hi rend="latintype">Palladio</hi></rs>. Ich würde mich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr freuen, dorthin von Dir eine Karte zu bekommen.</p><closer>Mit herzlichen Grüßen von meiner <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb17164">Frau</rs> u. mir <lb/>Dein <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
